# }

### Filtrar sanciones por tipo
GET {{baseUrl}}/sanctions?type=FINE
Authorization: Bearer {{accessToken}}

### Filtrar sanciones por estado
GET {{baseUrl}}/sanctions?status=PENDING
Authorization: Bearer {{accessToken}}

### Obtener sanciones activas
# @name getActive
GET {{baseUrl}}/sanctions/active
Authorization: Bearer {{accessToken}}

###
# Response esperado:
# {
#   "success": true,
#   "data": [
#     {
#       "id": "uuid-sanction",
#       "driverId": "uuid-driver",
